  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 11th level, you finally open your eyes to the world. You become immune to the blinded condition, gaining 60 feet of true sight, chakra sight, and darkvision.</p><p>Additionally, you can always tell when a creature is lying, and have advantage on Insight checks to discern a creature's intentions towards you. You can calculate Insight with Intelligence or Dexterity in place of Wisdom.</p><p>This increases to 120 feet of each sight at 15th level. Also at 15th level, you become immune to Genjutsu with the Visual or Auditory keywords. (Select one between the two.)</p>",
